      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Your feelings are entirely valid, and the journey of confronting such profound feelings is undoubtedly tough. Remember, the value in your struggle isn't necessarily in escaping the waves but in finding moments where you can breathe, even amidst the turbulence. Sometimes, through this struggle, we can foster connections, compassion, and even community. We don't always have to find meaning; we can find worth in our experiences, relationships, and growth. Are there any particular aspects of life where you've found even a small sense of worth or community?",
      "source": "target",
